    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 6th level, you gain the ability to cloak yourself in a fey magic that makes others want to serve you. As a bonus action, you cast @UUID[Compendium.renegados-compendium.magias.Item.059ykAUf9mtHLUqZ], without expending a spell slot, and you take on an appearance of unearthly beauty for 1 minute or until your @status[concentration] ends (as if you were @status[concentration||concentrating] on a spell). During this time, you can cast @UUID[Compendium.renegados-compendium.magias.Item.059ykAUf9mtHLUqZ] as a bonus action on each of your turns, without expending a spell slot.</p><p>Any creature &amp;Reference[condition=charmed] by you automatically fails its saving throw against the @UUID[Compendium.renegados-compendium.magias.Item.059ykAUf9mtHLUqZ] you cast with this feature.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
